{"tid":904883,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單用寫個read到mifare卡的php程式難唔難?","createTime":"2018-11-16T16:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T10:50:55.000Z","uid":107567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90ee2524fe4f3e72d3d9c72d372aad301460d2f0","tid":904883,"uid":107567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"read到張卡id, 可加資料入卡,改野<br />\n<br />\n已買左reader, 但唔識寫點將卡的資料show出來<br />\n<br />\n目的係要整到 NFC attendance system<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想搵sample都難"},{"pid":"8d9db6aa24f33d7e7b4b1f71e86d96a4e9def0fd","tid":904883,"uid":61347,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:55:46.000Z","msg":"以我既無知試下答你，有錯勿屌<br />\n<br />\nPHP 本身就係做Server-Side網頁為主要方向<br />\n如果係純PHP，唔用其他野<br />\n就想做晒你所講既Read, Write to NFC 應該唔得<br />\n（可能係我井底之蛙啦）<br />\n<br />\n大多數方向都係：<br />\nC/C++ NFC lib 讀/寫data 然後寫入去DB/File<br />\nPHP去掘返DB/File data出黎，再以網頁形式顯示出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果係純粹快趣起貨for交功課，上面既方向可能會易d快d<br />\n如果係學術研究，好堅持純PHP做晒全部野就祝你好運"},{"pid":"7f792e3ec0f192a5349082aa0cb4bec66392c7ad","tid":904883,"uid":113680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"乜野reader先?<br />\n如果用Serial Com出data嘅,可以用js拎啲data再post去php<br />\n定其實你講緊php-cli<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fe7551a7c2448cbc48d0046a959538393a270f","tid":904883,"uid":35092,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"我都嘗試做過，PHP 真係有好多限制。你要知道 PHP 係 server side language，係個 server 度 run，run 完 return 個 html （result）出來比 client display。<br />\n<br />\n但是不要 read / write 張卡，係需要透過 client 機上個 reader / writer 去操作。簡單D 來講，你要寫一個 server program 去 control 你 client 機上 device。幾乎純 php 係冇乜可能做到。（如果咁簡單就可以用一部機 control 到 client 機上 device，呢個 security 層面上已經唔允許你咁做）<br />\n<br />\n所以都係老老實實學下 C 啦 ..."},{"pid":"66c8b9065bf6b89ca598d34be5e864bee11d9f40","tid":904883,"uid":1402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07